Package: com.iforward.pushplus
Name: iForward-PushPlus
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Forward SMS, calls, and voicemails to PushPlus notification service. Supports dual SIM identification and works with iOS 14+.
 This tweak monitors your device for incoming/outgoing SMS, iMessages, calls, and voicemails, then forwards them to PushPlus (pushplus.plus) for real-time notifications.
 .
 Features:
 - SMS/iMessage forwarding with sender identification
 - Call notifications with duration tracking
 - Voicemail alerts
 - Dual SIM support (shows Account ID and Service type)
 - Contact name resolution from Address Book
 - Configurable notification subjects
 - Works in background via LaunchDaemon
 .
 Configuration: Settings â†’ iForward
 Requires: PushPlus account and token from https://www.pushplus.plus
Homepage: https://github.com/spacex-3/iForward-push
Maintainer: spacex-3 <fantasysk@qq.com>
Author: spacex-3 <fantasysk@qq.com>
Section: Utilities
Depends: firmware (>= 14.0), curl, sqlite3
Conflicts: com.iforward.original
Replaces: com.iforward.original
Priority: optional
Tag: purpose::daemon, role::enduser
